Why Two Sigma












Internships

We offer a 10-week paid summer internship program in SoHo, NYC. Interns will attend internal speaker series, game nights, 3D printing classes, presentation skills workshops, Broadway shows, and much more. In Quantitative Research and Software Engineering, you’ll own a single project during the course of your time with us. We’ll assign you a dedicated manager, and you’ll present your results at the end of the program.


          “I know my contributions matter. I could see the results of my work the first week I was here – not just on a project but in the real world.”
          
        



    See our job openings and available internships.
